Build a Canvas App in Power Apps connected to Dataverse to manage the Well 
Assurance process for an Oil & Gas company. The app uses the following 
Dataverse tables:

--- TABLES ---

1. coepp_pronostico (Forecast - Header)
   - Pronostico_ID (Text)
   - Pronostico_Fecha_Dttm (DateTime)
   - Pronostico_Etiqueta_Desc (Text)
   - Pronostico_Estado (Choice: Active | Inactive)

2. coepp_pronostico_detalles (Forecast - Details)
   - Pad_Hijo_Desc (Text)
   - Pozo_Padre_Nombre_Corto (Text)
   - Nivel_Calculado_Desc (Text)
   - Fluido_Pozo_Padre_Desc (Text)
   - Carga_Manual_Whpi_Ind (Text)
   - Presion_Inicial (Number)
   - Inc_Presion_Por_Frachit (Number)
   - Maxima_Presion_Esperada (Number)

3. coepp_casos (Cases - Header)
   - Caso_Nro (Text, auto-generated)
   - Pronostico_ID (Lookup to coepp_pronostico)
   - PronosticoPADHijo_Desc (Text)
   - Caso_Tipo (Choice: Case 3 | Case 2 | Case 1)
   - Caso_Estado (Choice: Draft | Open | Closed | Cancelled)
   - Caso_Fecha_Cierre (Date)

4. coepp_casos_detalles (Cases - Details, one record per Parent Well)
   - ID_Caso (Lookup to coepp_casos)
   - Pozo_Padre_Nombre_Corto (Text)
   - Pozo_Padre_Origen (Choice: Manual | Active Forecast)
   - Nivel_Calculado_Desc (Text)
   - Fluido_Pozo_Padre_Desc (Choice: GAS | NAFTA | OIL | OIL BS)
   - Carga_Manual_Whpi_Ind (Choice: YES | NO)
   - Presion_Inicial (Number)
   - Inc_Presion_Por_Frachit (Number, read-only unless Manual Load = YES)
   - Maxima_Presion_Esperada (Number, always read-only, calculated: Presion_Inicial + Inc_Presion_Por_Frachit)
   - Tipo_Aseguramiento (Choice: AB | AD | FP | NC)
   - Tipo_Pozo (Text)
   - Tipo_Intervencion (Choice: INT | REP | ISQ)
   - Orden_Interna_Nro (Number)
   - Justificacion (Text, mandatory when edited by Assurance role)

--- ROLES (via Azure AD Groups) ---
- Reservoir
- Assurance
- Production Engineering
- Management Control (CdG)
- P&L / Programming
- YAD / Geology / Others (read-only)

--- SCREENS ---

SCREEN 1 — Active Forecast / Child PADs
- Gallery with active Child PADs from the current active forecast
- Columns: Pad_Hijo_Desc, number of Parent Wells, number of active cases
- Free text search filter
- On select → navigate to Screen 2
- "Generate New Case" button visible only for Reservoir and Assurance roles
  - Enabled only if no case exists in Draft or Open status for that PAD
  - On click → create record in coepp_casos (Type=Case 3, Status=Draft), navigate to Screen 2

SCREEN 2 — Cases for a Child PAD
- Header with PAD and Forecast data
- Gallery with all cases for the selected PAD, sorted by date descending
- Columns: Caso_Nro, Caso_Tipo, Caso_Estado (color badge: Draft=gray, Open=green, Closed=navy, Cancelled=red), Created by, Date
- On select → navigate to Screen 3

SCREEN 3 — Case Detail
- Header: Caso_Nro, PAD, Case Type, Status badge, Forecast ID, Created by, Date
- "Change Status" button with logic:
  - Draft → Open: visible for Reservoir. Requires all Parent Wells to have Presion_Inicial filled.
  - Open → Closed: visible for Reservoir and Assurance.
  - Open → Cancelled: visible for Assurance only. Requires mandatory Justification field.
- Parent Wells section: expandable gallery showing coepp_casos_detalles for the case
- "Add Parent Well Manually" button: visible only if Status=Draft AND role=Reservoir or Assurance
- Delete button per row: visible only if Pozo_Padre_Origen=Manual AND Status=Draft
- Case comments section (free text, with date and user)
- "Notify P&L" button: visible for Reservoir/Assurance, only when Status=Open

SCREEN 4 — Parent Well Form (edit coepp_casos_detalles)
Field permissions by case status and user role:

| Field                   | Draft/Reservoir  | Open/ProdEng    | Open/CdG    | Open/Assurance         |
|------------------------|------------------|-----------------|-------------|------------------------|
| Pozo_Padre_Nombre_Corto | Editable         | Read-only       | Read-only   | Editable + Justif.     |
| Nivel_Calculado_Desc    | Editable         | Read-only       | Read-only   | Editable + Justif.     |
| Fluido_Pozo_Padre_Desc  | Editable         | Read-only       | Read-only   | Editable + Justif.     |
| Presion_Inicial         | Editable if Manual=YES | Read-only | Read-only | Editable + Justif.     |
| Inc_Presion_Por_Frachit | Read-only        | Read-only       | Read-only   | Read-only              |
| Maxima_Presion_Esperada | Read-only (calc) | Read-only       | Read-only   | Read-only              |
| Tipo_Aseguramiento      | Read-only        | Editable        | Read-only   | Editable + Justif.     |
| Tipo_Pozo               | Read-only        | Editable        | Read-only   | Editable + Justif.     |
| Tipo_Intervencion       | Read-only        | Editable        | Read-only   | Editable + Justif.     |
| Orden_Interna_Nro       | Read-only        | Read-only       | Editable    | Editable + Justif.     |
| Justificacion           | Hidden           | Hidden          | Hidden      | Mandatory if editing   |

Additional rules:
- CdG can only fill Orden_Interna_Nro if Tipo_Aseguramiento = AB or AD
- Maxima_Presion_Esperada = Presion_Inicial + Inc_Presion_Por_Frachit (always calculated, never editable)
- If Carga_Manual_Whpi_Ind = YES → Presion_Inicial editable for Reservoir in Draft status
- If Pozo_Padre_Origen = Manual → Justification mandatory for all roles on creation

--- KEY BUSINESS RULES ---
1. Only one case in Draft or Open status per Child PAD at a time.
2. To create a new Case 3: all previous cases for the PAD must be Closed or Cancelled.
3. If the latest case is Closed → next case to create is Case 2 (not Case 3).
4. If the latest case is Cancelled → a new Case 3 can be created.
5. On status change to Open (Locked): Parent Wells set is frozen (no add or delete allowed).
6. Structural fields (Well name, Level, Fluid, Origin) become read-only for all roles when Open.
7. Assurance can edit any field as contingency, but Justification is always mandatory.
8. On closing Case 3 → system automatically creates Case 2 for the same Child PAD.

--- POWER AUTOMATE NOTIFICATIONS ---
Create flows triggered from the app:

- On Open: email to CdG and Production Engineering (CC: Assurance)
  Subject: "Well Assurance - Case [No] - Case 3 – Open - PAD: [Child PAD] - Forecast ID: [ID]"

- On setting Tipo_Intervencion for a Parent Well: email to Programming and YAD

- On Cancelled: email to Reservoir and Geology (CC: Assurance)
  Subject: "Well Assurance - Case [No] - Case 3 – Cancelled - PAD: [Child PAD]"

- On Closed: email to Reservoir (CC: Assurance)
  Subject: "Well Assurance - Case [No] - Case 3 – Closed - PAD: [Child PAD]"

All emails include: table with case Parent Wells and "Access Application" button.
From: Plataforma365

